    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Computed RH values across all 5 operating points satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion at the settings used during validation (h_target = 0.15 mm, alpha_thresh = 0.785, epsilon_iter = 1e-5). The assessment team is satisfied that the CFD model provides adequate credibility to support the worst-case hemolysis identification decision for the Class II CPB device.",
